Package: SoccerStatsR
Title: Advanced Soccer Analytics and Performance Metrics
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gianluca", "Calvosa", , "gcalvosa12@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: 
    This package provides advanced soccer analytics, including player performance scoring, expected goals (xG) 
    calculation, win probability estimation, match summary generation, and player comparison. Ideal for 
    coaches, analysts, and sports enthusiasts looking to gain insights into soccer matches and player statistics.
